lines.text:
[repeated line, after a crash or fall]
I'm okay! I'm okay!
I'm telling you, I saw a ghost!
Tell it like it is, Bobby, and in the meantime would somebody mind calling me a taxi?
And where do you think you're going?
I'll be staying on vacation in Wakiki, Skeeter doesn't stay with dead folks.
Actually we're going to mid-town. We're going to the mall to buy some new socks. Can't ever have too many socks.
